      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "However, this isn’t a museum that’s all looking and no touching. The 90-acre campus acts as a kind of driving school for those wanting to learn how to drive a Ford Model T. Just because you can drive a modern car well doesn’t mean you know anything about these classics, which have no gas pedal but come with a hand lever and three foot pedals as well as two hand controls on the steering wheel.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Learning to drive a Ford Model T is an experience which will teach you to appreciate how far the user-friendly nature of cars ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "has progressed in the past century",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/features-3/henry-ford-quotes/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". It also helps anyone understand just how much skill driving an automobile required back in the day. Instruction lasts about 3 hours and you get to check out the museum for the rest of the day.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
